---
servings: 4
time: 15 minutes
difficulty: easy
cuisine: Mexican
tags: [corn, salad, quick, spicy]
title: Street Corn Salad
description: A simple grilled corn salad with cheese, spices, mayo, and lime for a street-food inspired side.
---

Cook @corn{4%cup} in a pan until browned. Once grilled, add @cojita cheese{0.5%cup} until slightly softened. Once softened, add @chili powder{1%tsp}, @cayenne pepper{1%tsp}, @mayo{1%tsp}, @lime{2%tbsp}, and @butter{1%tbsp}. Let cool slightly and serve. 
